{"tid":871713,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大係咪會愈易改變自己細個有嘅原則？","createTime":"2018-10-22T07:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:21:02.000Z","uid":89394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"676115c8070adc127af47543beb7f9886a82430e","tid":871713,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"例如我細個中學時覺得做飲食業好污糟，同自己講一定唔會做飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學時期因為想搵多啲錢，返炒散人工高，大學時期都咗返飲食一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畢業前後轉過唔同行業嘅長短工，結果都唔及我返番去大學第一間炒散果喥高人工同做得開心，最後而家變咗喺果喥做長工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （不過我做果個位唔洗點執下欄都乾淨啲）<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都會大大下為咗其他野妥協而放低咗原則？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c4226bb0eb64261a70f97f683fe65b3d2eeb5b","tid":871713,"uid":34005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"人會變 月會圓 變幻原是永恆"},{"pid":"8f4331481f239bc667914878a624955acb349274","tid":871713,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5c4226bb0eb64261a70f97f683fe65b3d2eeb5b","tid":871713,"uid":34005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"人會變 月會圓 變幻原是永恆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"我連自己有時都恥笑自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f003809f4a105aa0ea69ec3abb4a0854b55a21","tid":871713,"uid":167219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n以前誓不做飲食<br />\n宜家就搭緊車準備返餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26b1fdae08e40681e45880b03af530040afc523","tid":871713,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f003809f4a105aa0ea69ec3abb4a0854b55a21","tid":871713,"uid":167219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br